{"type": "article", "id": 25978, "title": "沐浴皂包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-26T07:35:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130819NfGA8ljbHxZJIWPo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是 <a href=\"http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.estudiomenta.mx%2F&amp;t=ZjQwNzRmYjQ1OWIwODk0ZTgwODAwYTVlMDA2MjMwNWU5MDZmMDk1NiwxdElIbkkyWQ%3D%3D\" target=\"_blank\">Menta</a> 为 Savon Stories 新的沐浴皂系列所设计的包装，清新细腻的插画表现了四种不同的香型，仿佛取自某个植物学家精心绘制的笔记。最外一圈品牌标签组成的系带是这款包装的点睛之笔，给人感觉像是打开了一个充满夏日气息的礼物盒。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130816yaXn8DPvWYpUAq3u.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130817ALqsHuOoxJ29Wm8M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130817qX8DQlcOU7WI6pT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130818luzrVYR9as6CdtNZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}